Åú Reduce this card's Level by the Level of the sent monster.During your opponent's Main Phase, you can: Immediately after this effect resolves, Synchro Summon 1 Synchro Monster, using Materials including this card you control (this is a Quick Effect). You can only Synchro Summon "Accel Synchron(s)" once per turn.

Once per turn, during the End Phase, if this card is in the Graveyard because it was sent there this turn: Take 1000 damage. When this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can target 1 "Blackwing" monster you control, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Increase its Level by 1.
Åú Reduce its Level by 1.You can only use this effect of "Blackwing - Decay the Ill Wind" once per turn.

Cannot be used as a Synchro Material. Up to twice per turn: You can target 1 "Constellar" monster on the field, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Increase its Level by 1.
Åú Reduce its Level by 1.

If this card attacks, at the end of the Damage Step: You can Tribute 1 other "Dinomist" monster, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú This card can attack an opponent's monster again in a row, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent.
Åú Shuffle 1 card from your opponent's hand (at random) or their side of the field into the Deck, then this card gains 100 ATK.

You can Tribute 1 other "Dinomist" monster, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú This card can attack your opponent directly this turn.
Åú This card can make a second attack during each Battle Phase this turn.

Up to twice per turn, if this card was Special Summoned by the effect of a "Dododo" monster this turn: You can target 1 "Dododo" monster you control, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Increase its Level by 1.
Åú Reduce its Level by 1.

Your opponent cannot target "Flower Cardian" monsters you control with card effects, also those monsters cannot be destroyed by card effects. During your opponent's Draw Phase, if they draw a card(s) for their normal draw: Inflict 1500 damage to your opponent. Once per turn, during your opponent's End Phase: Activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Skip the Draw Phase of your next turn.
Åú This card has its other effects negated until your opponent's next Standby Phase.

When this card declares an attack on an opponent's monster: This card gains 400 ATK for each EARTH Warrior-Type Synchro Monster you control, until the end of the Damage Step. When this card destroys an opponent's monster by battle and sends it to the Graveyard: You can activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Special Summon that monster to your side of the field.
Åú Take control of 1 face-up monster your opponent controls.

You can only use the following effect of "Junk Changer" once per turn. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can target 1 "Junk" monster on the field, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Increase its Level by 1.
Åú Reduce its Level by 1.

Once per turn: You can detach 1 Xyz Material from this card to activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Send 1 card from your Deck to the Graveyard.
Åú Choose 1 monster from your Deck and place it on top of your Deck.

You can discard this card, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Add 1 "Lunalight" monster from your Graveyard to your hand, except "Lunalight Black Sheep".
Åú Add 1 "Polymerization" from your Deck to your hand.If this card is sent to the Graveyard as a Fusion Material for a Fusion Summon: You can add to your hand, 1 face-up "Lunalight" Pendulum Monster from your Extra Deck or 1 "Lunalight" monster from your Graveyard, except "Lunalight Black Sheep".

You can banish this card from your Graveyard to activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Increase the Level of all "Mermail" monsters you currently control by 1.
Åú Increase the Level of all "Mermail" monsters you currently control by 2.

You can only use the effect of "Number 63: Shamoji Soldier" once per turn. You can detach 1 Xyz Material from this card, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú At the start of your opponent's next Standby Phase, each player draws 1 card.
Åú Each player gains 1000 Life Points.

If you have no Spell/Trap Cards in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). After this card was Special Summoned this way, you cannot Special Summon monsters for the rest of this turn, except "Superheavy Samurai" monsters. You can Tribute this card, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Destroy 1 card in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone, then you can Set the destroyed Spell/Trap Card on your side of the field.
Åú Destroy 1 card in your opponent's Pendulum Zone, then you can place the destroyed card in your Pendulum Zone.

Cannot attack the turn it is Summoned. While you control "Toon World" and your opponent controls no Toon monsters, this card can attack your opponent directly. Once per turn: You can discard 1 "Toon" card, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú Special Summon 1 Toon monster from your Deck, except "Toon Dark Magician", ignoring its Summoning conditions.
Åú Add 1 "Toon" Spell/Trap Card from your Deck to your hand.

Once per turn, during either player's turn: You can discard 1 "Ninja" monster, then activate 1 of these effects;
Åú This turn, "Ninja" monsters and "Ninjitsu Art" cards you control cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects.
Åú 1 "Ninja" monster you control gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.
